us and the services trade deficit) to analyze their long-term suppressive effect on the Yen exchange rate.\n\nProvide a strategic outlook for the Yen's trend in 2026 and identify core variables that may trigger a trend reversion or trend reversal for the Yen."}], 'model': 'nex/nex-n1.1', 'max_tokens': 2048, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.3}}
