2026-05-19 03:18:45 [DEBUG] openai._base_client: Request options: {'method': 'post', 'url': '/chat/completions', 'files': None, 'idempotency_key': 'stainless-python-retry-cb586097-4c30-4d2e-bee5-6051aef5bd00', 'security': {'bearer_auth': True}, 'content': None, 'json_data': {'messages': [{'role': 'system', 'content': '你是一位法律领域的资深专家，精通刑法、民商法、知识产权法、公司治理、国际私法、政府监管等方向。熟悉中国大陆、香港、美国、英国等多个法域的法律体系。\n\n回答要求：\n1. 明确适用的法律法规和司法解释\n2. 区分不同法域的规定差异\n3. 引用具体法条编号\n4. 分析法律关系和权利义务\n5. 考虑实务操作中的注意事项\n6. **必须给出明确、无歧义的结论**：在分析完所有争议点和理论分歧后，必须基于案情事实和主流法律理论，给出一个确定的结论（例如“成立”、“不成立”、“构成A罪而非B罪”），避免使用“有争议”、“更可能”等模糊表述。如果存在不同学说或判例立场，需在分析中说明，但最终结论必须明确。\n7. **在涉及因果关系、客观归责等核心争议时，必须结合具体案情细节（如被害人主动发起、反复蛇行、突然变向、醉酒状态等）进行逐层分析**，明确区分“自我答责的自我危害”与“他者危害”的界限，并据此判断是否切断客观归责。\n8. **在给出否定性结论（如“不构成某罪”）后，必须补充说明行为人的行为应如何定性**（例如构成其他罪名、属于行政违法、或无罪等），确保法律评价的完整性。\n\n## 注意事项\n- 引用法条时标明法律名称、条款编号\n- 区分法律规定和司法实践\n- 涉及案例分析需要指出核心争议焦点\n- 注意时效性，标注法律修订日期\n- 刑事案件注意程序法和实体法的交叉\n- 商事法律注意合规要求和监管动态\n'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': '## 题目\n[Restructuring / Financing / M&A] 任务 #11217\n\nYou are an attorney retained to provide legal services to an investment institution established in mainland China. The institution proposes to make an equity investment in a company located in Côte d’Ivoire (the “Target Company”) and has engaged a law firm to conduct legal due diligence.\n\nPlease, under the applicable laws, conduct a legal analysis of the following operational issues, identify legal risks (if any), and provide risk-mitigation recommendations:\n(1) The Target Company was incorporated in 2020 with registered capital of XOF 10,000,000. According to the company agreement and articles of association, Shareholder A holds 51% and Shareholder B holds 49%. On May 25, 2021, the Target Company completed registration with the Commercial and Personal Property Credit Register at the Abidjan Commercial Court, and the shareholders were registered accordingly.\n(2) Under the articles of association, the capital contribution deadline is December 31, 2024. The shareholders made cash contributions directly to the company’s bank account in the amounts of XOF 5,100,000 and XOF 4,900,000 on December 1, 2024 and December 20, 2024, respectively. As of December 31, 2025, the company’s net assets were XOF 4,900,000.\n(3) To date, the Target Company’s 2025 financial statements have been approved by the shareholders’ meeting.\n\nPlease write concisely and logically, and cite laws and regulations accurately.\n\n## 要求\n请根据题目内容，给出专业、完整、准确的回答。回答要有条理，论证充分，必要时引用具体数据或来源。'}], 'model': 'nex/nex-n1.1', 'max_tokens': 8192, 'temperature': 0.1}}
