munoprecipitation-Mass Spectrometry), and deglycosylation and adjustments to reducing/non-reducing conditions to confirm that the 140 kDa band is the true target and to identify the source of the 70 kDa band.'}], 'model': 'nex/nex-n1.1', 'max_tokens': 2048, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.3}}
