ing historical data, (b) subscribing to real-time prices, and (c) sending a derivatives buy order.\n\n5) Provide a system architecture design: list the main modules and their key functions, and include a diagram (or schematic) showing how modules interact.'}], 'model': 'nex/nex-n1.1', 'max_tokens': 2048, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.3}}
